  <summary date="2024-04-03T19:50:45Z" status="Introduced in House">No Vaccine Mandates in Higher Education Act

This bill prohibits an institution of higher education (IHE) from receiving federal funds if the IHE requires its students or staff to receive a COVID-19 vaccine as a condition of enrollment in or employment at the IHE or for receiving any benefit, service, or contract.</summary>
